Per-directory build + KAT commands (example):
cd API_PKC/Implementations/Reference_Implementation/Venom-128 && make clean && make && make KAT && ./KAT_KEM && make clean
cd API_PKC/Implementations/Reference_Implementation/Venom-192 && make clean && make && make KAT && ./KAT_KEM && make clean
cd API_PKC/Implementations/Reference_Implementation/Venom-256 && make clean && make && make KAT && ./KAT_KEM && make clean
cd API_PKC/Implementations/Reference_Implementation/Venom-384 && make clean && make && make KAT && ./KAT_KEM && make clean
cd API_PKC/Implementations/Reference_Implementation/Venom-512 && make clean && make && make KAT && ./KAT_KEM && make clean

Final submission root is API_PKC/.
